<h1 id="thumbnails" class="page-header">Thumbnails</h1>

<p class="lead">Extend Bootstrap's
  <a href="../css/#grid">grid system</a>with the thumbnail component to easily display grids of images, videos, text, and more.</p>

<h3 id="thumbnails-default">Default example</h3>
<p>By default, Bootstrap's thumbnails are designed to showcase linked images with minimal required markup.</p>
